{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四章\"石室奇人\"讲述萧秋水、唐方、铁星月、左丘超然、马竟终、文鬓霜六人合力对抗权力帮剑王屈寒山。六人全力出击仍无法突破屈寒山的剑围，被逼入地下石室。萧秋水率众退入洞中，柳千变追击被唐方暗器逼退。洞中众人分派任务，文鬓霜与马竟终留守洞口，其余四人深入探索地道。途中遭遇权力帮快刀地魔杜绝伏击，铁星月以口咬刀锋化解危机。众人在石室深处发现被四道困龙索锁住的老人——广西武林三山之一的檬江杜月山。杜月山被屈寒山囚禁三年，始终不肯交出檬江剑法。萧秋水打开机关救下杜月山，杜月山以一口痰水击退杜绝。杜月山将藏于鞋内的檬江剑谱托付给萧秋水，计划从洞口跃上引开屈寒山，掩护众人从后方逃生。然而萧秋水察觉杜绝可能已从后方打开通道，话音未落，杜绝果然从后现身，屈寒山率众从前方包抄而来，众人陷入腹背受敌的绝境。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有用的，这牢是用地母精英铁所造的，本是用来关那杜老鬼的……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "紧守洞口，或许有救！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "不必了，他们不出来，也是死定了，问题是……先把出口守紧再说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你叹气，他叹气，左丘小子也叹气，我就看不出有什么好叹气的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "那你又叹什么气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "我是叹肚子饿了；那个死老马给迷魂药我们吃，害得我午饭没吃，晚餐又打到洞里来，吃个屁！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "我叹气就是知道你肚子一饿就要放屁。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "老二，你又叹什么气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "看你们两个叹气，所以叹气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡扯什么？！不如去找东西吃，不然我就要放屁",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "别别别——有话好说，屁是放不得的，我们一离开这里，谁守洞口，万一他们都闯了进来，岂不糟透！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这里让我来守好了，你们去探看，小心这里还有别的入口，免得着了他们的道儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "text": "文前辈——",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也守在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "文前辈一人守这里，是不够的，多一个人好有个照应。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我意已决，要不是我，你们今日就不会落在这里，所以我守这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "这是我们强要你带我们来的，是我们累你——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们总要给我补偿的机会——不必多说，我意已决——你们早去早回就好！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心，可能有异兽！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "听声响不会太近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心戒备才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕什么！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地道里还有权力帮的人，他是十九人魔中的'快刀地魔'杜绝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "地道里只怕还有别的东西，我们且过去看看。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王八羔子，对付个老人竟要如此！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "谁说我老？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "你还不算老呀？！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "算你厉害，救你出来再跟你骂过！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "敢问老丈……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "兔崽子，少来假惺惺！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "此人给锁于此地，显然是与权力帮为敌才逼致的，而且武功必定不低，否则也无需如此重锁，我们先把他救下来再说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们究竟是谁？！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "晚辈乃是浣花剑派后人萧秋水……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "西楼么？！他儿子都那么大了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "屈寒山那老贼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "前辈，当下之急，是先解除你身上之铁链，不知前辈可有办法？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "这铁链若是可以折断，早给我震碎了，还用得着你们？！那儿倒是有开关掣，这链是嵌到骨头里去了，扯不开了，但石壁的扳子倒是活动的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "扳掣在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "在甬道里人处石壁上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去开！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "社月山，你可自由了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "屈寒山，你这个老匹夫！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "杜月山，留下你的剑谱，放你一条生路！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "你逼供我多少时日，都没有把剑法传给你，而今我还怕了你不成？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "自由难得，杜月山，不要再瞎拼了，莫忘记三年前你是在我剑下为困龙索所捆的，我的耐心是有限的，可不会再容你逞能了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "老匹夫，我要杀了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "那你上来呀！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "上就上，难道我怕了你不成！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我从你们来的洞口上去，我一上去你们就往后跑，石室尽头处有一活栓，掀开它就有恫口，上边就是屈寒山的卧房，从那儿可以出去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "老前辈不行，屈寒山武功很高，你从洞口跃上去，他猛下杀手",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我旨在引开他的注意力，好让你们逃出去，逃出去后好公布这老匹夫的恶行，总比全死在这里好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "论内功，我不如屈寒山，若论剑法，我不逊给这老匹夫，他窥视我'檬江剑法'已久，贪得无厌，想兼得各家之长，他之所以留我不杀，亦即想逼供我的剑法，却不知我把剑谱藏于鞋内。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "今日之战，我已三年来动剑，而且筋骨俱伤，三年折磨早不成、形，他们人多势众，单只一个屈寒山，我已然不敌。这剑谱留给你，你也是练剑的，浣花剑法正要檬江剑法以助。这剑谱，绝不能落在那剑魔手中！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "杜月山，你藏头缩尾，不敢上来是不是？！",
