      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "前辈……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你给我等着，我上来就收拾你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "决收起来，别婆婆妈妈的！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "前辈，我认为你这样出去，还是不妥，为何不引他下来，给予致命之一击呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "前边还有我们一位马兄弟在等，更有文鬓霜前辈，不如我们虚张声势，然后一起往后撤走吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙！要走，就大家，一，齐，走！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这就去叫他们来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "只是什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "后面既有出路，为何屈寒山他们不前后夹攻进来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "小女娃可真仔细！后边的出道只能在这里边旋开，上面是开不进来的，要下然，他们早就进来了：而前边你们进来的洞口，在里面的人是无法开关的；我毕竟被关在这儿三年了，三年来，对这里的情况，又焉有不知之理？！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "又什么不好！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "text": "适才杜绝两度暗算未逞，正往里边溜走，此刻岂不是正好可以打开后面的洞口，让权力帮的人进来？！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "杜月山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是！快去封锁！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jue",
      "speaker_name": "杜绝",
